类 TestRowProcessorEndpoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor.TestRowProcessorEndpoint

  • public class TestRowProcessorEndpoint
extends Object
    Verifies ProcessEndpoint works. The tested RowProcessor performs two scans and a read-modify-write.
